OL,3,CUK could record another warmest day of
OL,4,Cyear as temperatures up to 33C forecast
OL,6,FThe UK could break its record for the
OL,7,Fwarmest day of the year for the second
OL,8,Fday in a row, with temperatures up to
OL,9,F33C forecast.
OL,11,FTemperatures reached as high as 32.2C
OL,12,Fin Kew, west London, on Thursday, amid
OL,13,Fan amber heat-health alert for all
OL,14,Fregions in England.
OL,16,FThe alert, issued by the UK Health
OL,17,FSecurity Agency (UKHSA) for the first
OL,18,Ftime since September 2023, is in force
OL,19,Funtil 9am on Monday.
