OL,3,CUK could record another warmest day of
OL,4,Cyear as temperatures up to 33C forecast
OL,6,FIt warns "significant impacts are
OL,7,Flikely" across health and social care
OL,8,Fservices because of high temperatures,
OL,9,Fincluding a rise in deaths,
OL,10,Fparticularly among those aged 65 and
OL,11,Fover or people with health conditions.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, temperatures are forecast
OL,14,Fto reach the low 30s and could
OL,15,Fpotentially hit 33C on Friday, the Met
OL,16,FOffice said.
OL,18,FAnd by Friday afternoon a number of
OL,19,Fareas are expected to have passed the
OL,20,Fheatwave criteria, Met Office weather
OL,21,Fforecaster Dan Stroud said.
