OL,3,CUK could record another warmest day of
OL,4,Cyear as temperatures up to 33C forecast
OL,6,FAn official heatwave is recorded when
OL,7,Fareas reach a certain temperature for
OL,8,Fthree consecutive days, with
OL,9,Fthresholds varying from 25C to 28C in
OL,10,Fdifferent parts of the UK.
OL,12,FMr Stroud said: "We're expecting the
OL,13,Fhot and dry conditions to continue, it
OL,14,Fdoes turn a little bit hazier in the
OL,15,Fwest during the course of Friday,
OL,16,Fwe're still expecting temperatures to
OL,17,Freach the low 30s, 31C, 32C fairly
OL,18,Fwidely, maybe seeing 33C."
