OL,3,CUK could record another warmest day of
OL,4,Cyear as temperatures up to 33C forecast
OL,6,FIncreasing amounts of cloud will move
OL,7,Fin from the west on Saturday, with a
OL,8,Fchance of showers, some which could be
OL,9,Fthundery in North Wales and north-west
OL,10,FEngland, while eastern areas will see
OL,11,Fanother dry and hot day, he added.
OL,13,FTemperatures will be in the low 30s,
OL,14,Fand probably be the peak of the hot
OL,15,Fspell on Saturday, as 34C is possible,
OL,16,Fstill below the June record of 35.6C
OL,17,Fin 1976.
