OL,6,FSunday will be another very warm day
OL,7,Fin the south and east probably in the
OL,8,Flate 20s, elsewhere it will be cooler,
OL,9,Fwith temperatures in the mid 20s, Mr
OL,10,FStroud said.
OL,12,FIt comes after a warning has been
OL,13,Fissued as firefighters have responded
OL,14,Fto more than 500 wildfires across
OL,15,FEngland and Wales this year so far.
