OL,3,CUK could record another warmest day of
OL,4,Cyear as temperatures up to 33C forecast
OL,6,FAs of Thursday, 564 wildfire incidents
OL,7,Fhave been responded to by English and
OL,8,FWelsh fire and rescue services so far
OL,9,Fthis year, which is a 717% increase on
OL,10,Fthe same period in 2024, and more than
OL,11,Fdouble the number seen in 2022 which
OL,12,Fwent on to be the worst year on record
OL,13,Ffor wildfires, the National Fire
OL,14,FChiefs Council (NFCC) said.
OL,16,FThe NFCC is now urging caution among
OL,17,Fmembers of the public when enjoying
OL,18,Fthe outdoors in a bid to prevent
OL,19,Ffurther spikes in incidents.
